She is roped around the wrists, chest, and knees, leaving a tiny bit of movement for her high-heeled feet on the small shelf. A thick cleave gag muffles her.

title: Velvet Allure
description: Fay is wearing an elegant, long, black velvet dress with matching high heels. She is sitting on the couch, cleave-gagged, with her hands bound above her head, and the same rope that ties them running underneath the sofa to her bound ankles.

title: Voluntary Hostage
description: Brave Alais Peach volunteers to be the hostage in exchange for the others. She promises not to run or scream, but her captor has other ideas, and ties her up tightly, as well as gagging her with a large silk scarf.

title: Wait Here A While
description: Jewell Marceau is strapped to an ornate and heavy chair, bound with plenty of red rope. The cleave-gag in her mouth prevents her from complaining about the uncomfortable and powerless way her wrists are tied to the chair's back.

title: Waiting For Her Purpose
description: Lex is kneeling alone in a room, with her hands tied to opposite walls, and her ankles bound together. She is further silenced by a cleave-gag.

title: Why Me, Part 2
description: Dominick is in her underwear. Her arms are spread apart and tied to metal fixtures. She is cleave-gagged. This is the conclusion of the story, and the mysterious captors with their terrifying eyes come for her again.

title: Why Me?
description: Dominick finds herself at the hands of terrifying captors with an air of the supernatural about them. As she muses her predicament, chained and manacled, she suddenly jumps to action in an attempt to free herself. But then one of her captors enters, and Dominick faints, only to wake up in stricter bondage.

title: Wrapped Around Post
description: With her back to the post, and her arms entangled in ropes behind her back, Raevan is tightly bound and cannot move. She is wearing black leggings and a corset, and is gagged with a cloth.

title: Writer's Block
description: In this video, Raevan is having a little trouble with her writing assignment. To help her get into the spirit of things, she decides a little roleplay is in order. Suddenly, her mind wanders to a pole-tied damsel in peril...

title: Writer's Block 2
description: Raevan has writer's block. To give her inner muse a little push, she has decided to try writing whilst handcuffed. The story she dreams up this time involves leopard print underwear, a ballgag and chains, all on a hunt gone wrong.

title: Writer's Block, Part 3
description: In a final attempt to find inspiration for her bondage story, Raevan decides to get into costume. She dons a long and tight red rubber dress, satin opera gloves and high heels, before handcuffing herself. Finally the creative juices are flowing, and she imagines herself tied to a cross.

title: Wrongfully Accused And Sentenced
description: In this gripping tale we find Dominick sentenced to hard labour for a crime she didn't commit. Shackled in irons, Dominick is dragged behind a horse to the prison camp. She spends her days grinding a wheel with a fellow prisoner, chained and manacled. After countless days of unforgiving labour, Dominick seizes her chance and attempts an escape. But will she get far?

title: Wrongfully Accused And Sentenced, Part 2
description: In part two of this story, prisoner Dominick is made to endure a lengthy bondage torment for her escape attempt, which sees her standing precariously on her tiptoes while her arms are spread and tied to a frame above. Afterwards, it's back to the grinding wheel, but she sees a second opportunity for escape, and manages to arm herself too. But will it end well?
